{"tid":694404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賤種卡華積鐵定無緣世界盃首戰 他連路都走不了","createTime":"2018-06-08T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T22:42:39.000Z","uid":20634,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"948423f9e5c7e211e3f68dc70bbf849719c09350","tid":694404,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/06/08/5/518f7e398eefa439f67db6776f6fe10b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F5%2F518f7e398eefa439f67db6776f6fe10b.jpg&h=51cc6e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　根據《阿斯報》報導，雖然西班牙國家隊教練盧比迪古期待卡華積趕上世界盃首戰，但是球員的身邊人對此持悲觀態度。<br />\n<br />\n　　《阿斯報》稱卡華積的情況依然不明朗，盧比迪古曾在接受基比電台的採訪時表示：「卡華積會為了趕上首場比賽而努力的。」但是，《阿斯報》稱卡華積的身邊人對此持悲觀態度，他們不認為皇馬邊衛能夠趕上西班牙與葡萄牙的小組賽。卡華積的目標應該是盡力趕上球隊與伊朗的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n　　卡華積是在歐冠盃決賽上受傷的，西班牙國腳的大腿半腱肌輕微撕裂，當時西媒預計他將缺席2-3周。<br />\n<br />\n《阿斯報》稱近日西班牙新首相柏度-山齊士造訪國家隊訓練營時，卡華積還無法以完全正常的姿態行走。"},{"pid":"4c7fabf897459a80c38f42c84ba4bfd8110d61a5","tid":694404,"uid":32832,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n我利又嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a463562617dc2dd311a4f7359a6c424611694da1","tid":694404,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9d7db75edb284202e21f41715591c02d980916","tid":694404,"uid":12660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d4c28509805c7685b56813b7aabb7156357d89","tid":694404,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"cit